# NFL Survivor Pool Optimizer - Environment Variables

# The Odds API Configuration
# Get your free API key at: https://the-odds-api.com/
# Free tier includes 500 requests/month
ODDS_API_KEY=your_api_key_here

# NFL Season Configuration
# By default, CURRENT_SEASON and CURRENT_WEEK are automatically detected based on today's date
